.DT
can_wear_or_remove
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
can_wear_or_remove

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
can_wear_or_remove -  This method returns whether or not a player can wear or remove a given item.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs mixed can_wear_or_remove(object thing,
object player,
int flag)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the item to be worn or removed.
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the person doing the wearing or removing.
%^BOLD%^flag%^RESET%^ - if the flag is 1, the objects that won't allow
to remove the item are returned instead of a string.
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the reason why the item can't be removed, if there is one,
or the objects that aren't allowing to remove the item,
if the flag is true

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/clothing_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns whether or not a player can wear or remove a given item.
.EP

